OL,3,CSunak says Craig Williams bet on
OL,4,CGeneral Election 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FRishi Sunak said it was "very
OL,7,Fdisappointing" that one of his closest
OL,8,Fparliamentary aides had placed a bet
OL,9,Fon the date of the General Election
OL,10,Fjust days before the Prime Minister
OL,11,Fcalled it.
OL,13,FCraig Williams, who served as Mr
OL,14,FSunak's parliamentary private
OL,15,Fsecretary and is the Conservative
OL,16,Fcandidate for Montgomeryshire and
OL,17,FGlyndwr, has apologised but refused to
OL,18,Fsay whether he placed the bet on the
OL,19,Fbasis of insider information.
