OL,3,CSunak says Craig Williams bet on
OL,4,CGeneral Election 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister also declined to
OL,7,Fsay whether Mr Williams knew when
OL,8,Fpolling day would be when he put money
OL,9,Fon it, saying it would be
OL,10,Finappropriate to comment while the
OL,11,FGambling Commission investigates the
OL,12,Fmatter.
OL,14,FMr Williams, who was the Tory MP for
OL,15,FMontgomery until the election was
OL,16,Fcalled, is alleged to have placed a
OL,17,F#100 bet on a July polling day some
OL,18,Fthree days before Mr Sunak named the
OL,19,Fdate as July 4, at a Ladbrokes in his
OL,20,Fconstituency.
