OL,3,CSunak says Craig Williams bet on
OL,4,CGeneral Election 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FHe said on Thursday: "I clearly made a
OL,7,Fhuge error of judgment, that's for
OL,8,Fsure, and I apologise."
OL,10,FAsked about the case while attending
OL,11,Fthe G7 summit in Puglia, the Prime
OL,12,FMinister told broadcasters: "It's very
OL,13,Fdisappointing news and you will have
OL,14,Fseen Craig Williams say that it was a
OL,15,Fhuge error of judgment. Now, there's
OL,16,Fan independent inquiry that is
OL,17,Fongoing, which is necessarily
OL,18,Fconfidential, as well as independent.
OL,19,FAnd you'll appreciate that, given
OL,20,Fthat, it wouldn't be appropriate for
OL,21,Fme to comment while that's ongoing."
