OL,6,FPressed on what Mr Williams knew at
OL,7,Fthe time of the bet, Mr Sunak repeated
OL,8,Fthat "it wouldn't be right for me to
OL,9,Fcomment" while the probe is being
OL,10,Fcarried out.
OL,12,FMr Williams said on Wednesday that he
OL,13,Fwas facing a Gambling Commission
OL,14,Finvestigation, writing on social media
OL,15,Fthat he would "fully co-operate" with
OL,16,F"some routine inquiries".
