OL,3,CSunak says Craig Williams bet on
OL,4,CGeneral Election 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FAsked repeatedly whether he had had
OL,7,Finsider information, Mr Williams told
OL,8,Fthe BBC on Thursday: "I will not be
OL,9,Fexpanding on that statement because
OL,10,Fit's an independent process. The
OL,11,FGambling Commission are looking at it
OL,12,Fnow."
OL,14,FAs a parliamentary aide, Mr Williams
OL,15,Facted as a go-between for the Prime
OL,16,FMinister and his MPs, and is
OL,17,Funderstood to be a trusted member of
OL,18,FMr Sunak's team.
OL,20,FThe Guardian reported that the bet
OL,21,Fwould have led to a payout of #500.
